{
  "stem": "11296.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They was building the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So all the bricks that we took down from the houses and we cleaned, the men came to us, and took this away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we went from one house to the next, until we used up all the houses there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they took us to another place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So between, [INAUDIBLE], you know, men came in-- the French Jews, other Jews, there was a-- there was a couple there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, you know, he was, you know, talking to us, saying just about nobody-- nobody could-- just with our eyes, we was communicating with our eyes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was very nice, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Sometimes he brought something he picked up from his pocket, because he was working over the dead, so always found something to eat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So sometimes we got, you know-- we was working for Polish guys.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But other one gave us an onion, one gave us a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we start making contact with people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So after this, you know, after this kommando, we start going, yeah-- the weather start getting a little warmer, we start going out to another kommando.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this, I could not understand-- we was making roads-- roads.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This was like all around Birkenau-Auschwitz there was no roads, because it was farmland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So they was living in villas, the Germans, and they was driving the automobiles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They needed a road.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So they brought [INAUDIBLE] trucks, and they opened up the trucks, and everything came down like coal.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Go ahead.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like coal, and material.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I picked up this material, I said, why is this so sticky?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sticky material.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the guy told us, the bones from the dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was big, big pieces, so we had to take our hammers and crush it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We was making roads.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
